title: NEW Remodeled, Corner, Large 1BD on top of QA, 2 blks from Kerry Park
posting_body: ['Looking for a great 1 bedroom at a great price?!?!', "This newly remodeled apartment home has all the new finishes you're looking for in a GREAT location only steps away from Kerry Park on historic Queen Anne.", 'This is also a corner unit that has no direct neighbors on either side of the unit!', '- Brand new gorgeous wood-style flooring', '- Spacious living area, bedroom and HUGE closets', '- Large, storm AND sound-proof windows that look out to charming tree-lined street and QA Anne Ave', '- True city living!', 'Sleepless in Seattle vibes!', '- Corner windows are bright, sunny and cheery in the morning!', '- Cable ready', '- On-site manager', '- Private storage units in basement', '- Private bike storage room', '- Private carport parking available for an additional $150/month', '- Parking on all streets is FREE and NOT zoned', '- Secured entry-building with call box', '- Elevator', '- Cats ok ($300 deposit).', 'Cats ONLY', '- 3 block walk to all the shops/restaurants on the top of Queen Anne', '- EXCELLENT transit access: 1-2 blocks from various bus line stops to access downtown', '- Microsoft Connector picks up outside front door!', '- 3 min drive to', 'Highway 99 and I5 freeway access', 'W/S/G $85/month for first tenant; $135 for two', 'Tenant pays electric directly to Seattle City Light.', 'Please email to set up a showing ASAP before this apartment opportunity passes you by!', 'We do not accept Comprehensive Reusable Tenant Screening Reports as defined by and pursuant to RCW 59.18.', 'Equal Housing Opportunity.', 'Income verification must be provided showing a gross monthly income of 2.5x the monthly rent, a minimum credit score of 700, and no history of rental eviction.', 'Complete screening details can be found on the rental application prior to applying.']
